You can make out a fridge. The fridge contains a yellow bell pepper and a red onion. You can see a closed oven. You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a table. On the counter you can make out a banana and a cookbook. You can make out a stove. The stove appears to be empty. It would have been so cool if there was stuff on the stove.

There is an open frosted-glass door leading west. There is an exit to the east. You need an exit without a door? You should try going south.
